# LK21 API Endpoints

Here is the complete list of available endpoints for the **LK21 Provider**.

## 1. System Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/` | Root message (Health Check). |
| `POST` | `/register` | Register a new Cloudflared Tunnel URL. |
| `GET` | `/proxy` | Universal P2P/HLS Proxy with Header Injection. |

## 2. Default Routes (Backward Compatibility)
*These routes automatically default to the `lk21` provider.*

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/movies?page=N` | Get latest movies (Page default: 1). |
| `GET` | `/search?q=query` | Search for movies. |
| `GET` | `/watch/:slug` | Get stream details & auto-proxied links for a movie slug. |

## 3. Dynamic Provider Routes (Explicit)
*You can access LK21 explicitly using these routes.*

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/lk21/movies?page=N` | Get latest movies for LK21. |
| `GET` | `/lk21/search?q=query` | Search movies on LK21. |
| `GET` | `/lk21/watch/:slug` | Get stream details for LK21. |

---

### Example Usage

**Latest Movies (Page 1):**
`https://<worker-url>/movies`

**Search "Avatar":**
`https://<worker-url>/search?q=avatar`

**Watch "Avatar 2025":**
`https://<worker-url>/watch/avatar-fire-ash-2025`
